Where it all begin.
You heard that, if you follow the coast to the north, you will find the port of Souliac.

The small city of Souliac,
Everything is pacefull here.
The locals fear the black water that can be found eastward, and so do not like the inhabitant of Swaristant north from here.

A beautiful island at the center of the Narrow sea.
Rumor say that best potatoes are in Der Pellimare, South of here.

The nearby black water make the street of Swaristant unconfortable.
Locals wish for Radish from the south-west island of Vanvira.

The south of the Narrow sea,
The locacs all want to sell you there potatoes: they are the best in the known world.
